What you need to know:  Given the state of the race today, I believe Deputy President William Ruto will be among those for whom August 9 will be akin to Armageddon.If Mr Ruto loses – as I believe he will – he’ll be disconnected from the official money, power, and resource supply for the first time in a quarter century.Mr Ruto will suffer withdrawal symptoms like a ganja addict suddenly cut off from his dealer.